00:42:41,640 --> 00:42:44,640
Oh why are you like this, I did not do anything.

514
00:42:44,640 --> 00:42:46,490
Then why did you run away?

515
00:42:46,490 --> 00:42:49,470
You suddenly came after me so I ran!

516
00:42:50,410 --> 00:42:53,390
I get it, so just come down for a moment.

517
00:42:53,390 --> 00:42:56,040
Come down? Why would I come down?!

518
00:42:59,050 --> 00:43:03,280
That song. Why are you spreading that song?

519
00:43:03,280 --> 00:43:05,760
I'm not going to tell you.

520
00:43:08,970 --> 00:43:12,070
If you feel it's unfair then come up!

521
00:43:12,070 --> 00:43:13,960
Ah, that stings.

522
00:43:25,090 --> 00:43:28,810
What is your reason for spreading that song?

523
00:43:29,630 --> 00:43:31,940
This could be a big crime. Do you know that?

524
00:43:31,940 --> 00:43:34,680
What? A crime?

525
00:43:35,310 --> 00:43:40,800
Aigo, please save me. I also did this by request.

526
00:43:42,920 --> 00:43:44,060
What request?

527
00:43:44,060 --> 00:43:49,150
Yes, I'm a merchant that goes around from market to market.

528
00:43:49,150 --> 00:43:53,550
Then some guy said he will give me silvers if I spread this market-to-market, so

529
00:43:53,550 --> 00:43:55,730
that is why I did it.

530
00:43:55,730 --> 00:43:57,460
Who is the one that made you do it?

531
00:43:57,460 --> 00:43:59,400
The name I also do not know.

532
00:43:59,400 --> 00:44:04,420
Someone with an aura... He was a very elderly man.

533
00:44:04,420 --> 00:44:09,070
Oh, that man also gave me a silver like this.

534
00:44:12,070 --> 00:44:13,670
Baekmae Hwa!

535
00:44:13,670 --> 00:44:14,980
What is this?

536
00:44:14,980 --> 00:44:19,580
It is a silver, named baekmae hwa, that the Lee In Gyeom family uses.

537
00:44:22,490 --> 00:44:25,590
Where did you meet the man?

538
00:44:25,590 --> 00:44:27,560
It's not Gaegyeong, right?

539
00:44:28,140 --> 00:44:30,600
N, it's not Gaegyeong...

540
00:44:30,600 --> 00:44:33,950
It should be Gyungsanbu. Is it Gyungsanbu?

541
00:44:33,950 --> 00:44:36,210
Yes that's correct.

542
00:44:36,210 --> 00:44:40,100
I got the request five days ago at Gyungsanbu.

543
00:44:40,690 --> 00:44:43,630
Lee In Gyeom, that man....

544
00:44:45,060 --> 00:44:47,460
Listen carefully.

545
00:44:47,460 --> 00:44:51,490
Since you put someone else as the king and sang a song that puts down the king,

546
00:44:51,490 --> 00:44:53,960
you will be treated as a criminal.

547
00:44:53,960 --> 00:44:55,040
What?

548
00:44:55,040 --> 00:44:58,910
But, if you help us

549
00:44:59,640 --> 00:45:02,040
I'll give you wealth.

550
00:45:02,040 --> 00:45:03,610
Wealth?

551
00:45:04,410 --> 00:45:07,390
Oh, if you give me wealth then...

552
00:45:07,390 --> 00:45:10,190
Would you be able to testify?

553
00:45:10,190 --> 00:45:13,250
Then the Lee family of Junjoo

554
00:45:13,250 --> 00:45:16,010
will save your life.

555
00:45:16,010 --> 00:45:20,340
Oh, if you give me a lot of wealth

556
00:45:20,340 --> 00:45:22,870
do not worry about that testimony.

557
00:45:22,870 --> 00:45:26,150
That merchant has confessed.

558
00:45:27,210 --> 00:45:30,770
For spreading that song

559
00:45:30,770 --> 00:45:33,090
he received this.

560
00:45:33,860 --> 00:45:38,330
Isn't this baekmaehwa that is used in the Lee In Gyeom family?

561
00:45:38,330 --> 00:45:40,220
So it's Lee In Gyeom.

562
00:45:40,220 --> 00:45:43,990
Yes, it's Lee In Gyeom. Lee In Gyeom, that guy, even when he is exiled

563
00:45:43,990 --> 00:45:45,890
he is secretly planning things.

564
00:45:45,890 --> 00:45:48,740
From the start he did seem like he was a person that wouldn't back down that easily.

565
00:45:48,740 --> 00:45:51,640
That is why a lot of Sadaebu people, and other's of the same mind,

566
00:45:51,640 --> 00:45:53,990
wanted Lee In Gyeom to receive the death penalty.

567
00:45:53,990 --> 00:45:58,610
Teacher... Are you going to let Lee In Gyeom go like this?

568
00:45:59,580 --> 00:46:03,240
The merchant said he will confess anything if we give him wealth.

569
00:46:03,240 --> 00:46:05,680
Do you think you can arrest Lee In Gyeom?

570
00:46:08,450 --> 00:46:11,940
The reason would be for making commotion in the court by spreading the prophecy

571
00:46:11,940 --> 00:46:14,620
and alienating the returned generals.

572
00:46:15,530 --> 00:46:18,770
You go to Gyungsanbu with the soldiers and find evidence

573
00:46:18,770 --> 00:46:20,730
and arrest Lee In Gyueom right away.

574
00:46:20,730 --> 00:46:21,710
Yes.

575
00:46:21,710 --> 00:46:23,920
I'll go as well.

576
00:46:25,550 --> 00:46:31,620
There is something I have to resolve with Lee In Gyeom for the last time.

577
00:46:33,140 --> 00:46:36,410
The Lee family is becoming the king (prophecy)...

578
00:46:37,010 --> 00:46:40,670
Lee Seong Gye is not a person to do that.

579
00:46:40,670 --> 00:46:42,880
However, Jeong Do Jeon...

580
00:46:43,510 --> 00:46:48,150
I do not know what he is thinking.

581
00:46:49,360 --> 00:46:51,150
My lord.

582
00:46:52,790 --> 00:46:57,060
There is a message. They said it's from Hap Ha Lee In Gyeom.

583
00:46:57,060 --> 00:46:59,960
From Gwangpyung Buwungoon (his position)?

584
00:47:13,670 --> 00:47:17,280
Nonetheless, the public sentiment has completely gone over to Lee Seong Gye.

585
00:47:17,280 --> 00:47:20,860
Lee Seong Gye even has Haedong Gapjok as his in-law.

586
00:47:20,860 --> 00:47:23,310
Is is okay for Jung Chang,

587
00:47:23,310 --> 00:47:26,860
who Lee Seong Gye recommended to be a king, like this?

588
00:47:30,700 --> 00:47:35,110
My lord, some man brought a message.

589
00:47:35,110 --> 00:47:36,570
What do you mean by some man?

590
00:47:36,570 --> 00:47:40,360
He just said to send it to you quickly.

591
00:47:57,710 --> 00:48:00,550
Oh, General Jo?

592
00:48:01,700 --> 00:48:04,220
Why are you here?

593
00:48:04,220 --> 00:48:07,540
I came here after receiving Lee In Gyeom's message.

594
00:48:07,540 --> 00:48:12,390
Yes, I also came right after I got the message.

595
00:48:12,390 --> 00:48:14,250
Anyway, let's go inside

596
00:48:14,250 --> 00:48:15,870
Let's do that.

597
00:48:26,760 --> 00:48:28,790
Your Highness.

598
00:48:29,550 --> 00:48:32,730
Why are you here Your Highness?

599
00:48:32,730 --> 00:48:34,620
After receiving Gwang Pyung Goon's (Lee In Gyeom) letter

600
00:48:34,620 --> 00:48:38,620
I came here quickly and secretly at this late hour.

601
00:48:38,620 --> 00:48:42,620
Perhaps, is that how both of you guys came as well?

602
00:48:43,640 --> 00:48:45,840
That is right Your Highness.

603
00:48:45,840 --> 00:48:47,820
This is a strange thing.

604
00:48:47,820 --> 00:48:50,260
I did not see the man Lee In Gyeom sent

605
00:48:50,260 --> 00:48:54,060
but only found this here.

606
00:48:55,760 --> 00:48:57,780
木克日

607
00:48:57,780 --> 00:48:59,430
This is?

608
00:48:59,430 --> 00:49:02,110
The sun puts the tree in huge pain?

609
00:49:03,100 --> 00:49:05,250
What does this mean?

610
00:49:05,250 --> 00:49:07,880
This is a word ligature (when two or more two or more letters are joined as a single glyph).

611
00:49:07,880 --> 00:49:10,020
It's a secret code.

612
00:49:10,020 --> 00:49:14,170
Then can you solve it?

613
00:49:18,150 --> 00:49:21,460
This is probably...

614
00:49:23,550 --> 00:49:26,440
Chang

615
00:49:26,440 --> 00:49:28,510
Guk

616
00:49:28,510 --> 00:49:33,850
Lee

617
00:49:33,850 --> 00:49:38,460
Chang Guk Lee?

618
00:49:42,660 --> 00:49:45,160
Change wins over Lee?

619
00:49:46,180 --> 00:49:47,850
Perhaps?

620
00:49:49,190 --> 00:49:54,240
When did say we are meeting Her Highness and giving her our opinions?

621
00:49:54,240 --> 00:49:56,990
It is five days from now, but there is a strange rumor

622
00:49:56,990 --> 00:49:59,800
so It seems like we have to move the date up.

623
00:49:59,800 --> 00:50:03,640
Are you talking about that prophecy rumor?

624
00:50:03,640 --> 00:50:06,960
Is that really what Lee In Gyeom spread?

625
00:50:06,960 --> 00:50:10,340
From what we have found out so far, it seems like it.

626
00:50:10,340 --> 00:50:12,920
I have sent Nam Eun to Gyungsanbu.

627
00:50:12,920 --> 00:50:14,940
If it is Lee In Gyeom,

628
00:50:14,940 --> 00:50:17,730
this time he won't be able to escape.

629
00:50:17,730 --> 00:50:19,590
Only if that happens...

630
00:50:19,590 --> 00:50:23,570
Under no circumstance can we drag things out any longer.

631
00:50:23,570 --> 00:50:25,520
Before they think of something else,

632
00:50:25,520 --> 00:50:29,000
we have to send in a document, today, declaring Jung Chang as the new king

633
00:50:29,000 --> 00:50:30,950
and get the confirmation.

634
00:50:30,950 --> 00:50:32,280
I got it.

635
00:50:35,080 --> 00:50:39,850
The Left Shi Joong has gone to receive Her Highness's royal decree.

636
00:50:39,850 --> 00:50:45,090
As soon as the Left Shi Joong returns, we'll begin the Do Dang meeting.

637
00:51:06,290 --> 00:51:09,330
Her Highness' royal decree has been received.

638
00:51:11,750 --> 00:51:15,990
I will relay the decree to the Do Dang members.

639
00:51:25,000 --> 00:51:30,420
"To the members of Do Dang, who are the highest ranking officials in the great Goryeo, and also the foundation of the government,

640
00:51:30,420 --> 00:51:33,620
I send you the will of the royal family."

641
00:51:35,180 --> 00:51:39,400
Lee In Gyeom's residence in Gyeongsanboo

642
00:51:39,400 --> 00:51:43,900
This is where Lee In Gyeom is in exile?

643
00:51:43,900 --> 00:51:47,030
How can this be the criminal's place of exile?

644
00:51:47,030 --> 00:51:53,630
To think the who committed evil deeds all his life has been sitting here comfortably, planning a conspiracy instead of repenting his sins.

645
00:51:53,630 --> 00:51:55,990
Now that will be over too.

646
00:51:56,870 --> 00:52:00,750
Come here! Come here!

647
00:52:06,230 --> 00:52:07,950
What is it?

648
00:52:07,950 --> 00:52:10,640
I have come from the police office in Gaegyeong.

649
00:52:10,640 --> 00:52:14,380
This is criminal Lee In Gyeom's place of exile, yes?

650
00:52:14,380 --> 00:52:15,860
Yes, that is so.

651
00:52:15,860 --> 00:52:18,100
Make a path!

652
00:52:24,530 --> 00:52:27,990
Criminal Lee In Gyeom come out at once and receive the criminal's rope!

653
00:52:27,990 --> 00:52:31,110
What are you saying?

654
00:52:31,110 --> 00:52:34,710
What do you mean? Did you not hear?

655
00:52:34,710 --> 00:52:35,960
Criminal Lee In Gyeom—

656
00:52:35,960 --> 00:52:37,790
He passed away fifteen days ago.

657
00:52:37,790 --> 00:52:40,810
How can he obey the order?

658
00:52:42,200 --> 00:52:43,710
What?

659
00:52:43,710 --> 00:52:47,630
"Fortunately, the misguided Choi Yeong has been expelled,

660
00:52:47,630 --> 00:52:52,210
and the king is reflecting on his mistakes and is abdicating the throne of his own accord."

661
00:52:52,210 --> 00:52:55,290
"Isn't this the result of the court's goodwill."

662
00:52:57,050 --> 00:53:05,670
"Therefore, the continuation of the great Goryeo, and the restoration of the business of the common people, and the government

663
00:53:07,100 --> 00:53:09,300
will be carried by Crown Prince Chang"

664
00:53:11,960 --> 00:53:17,780
"His responsibilities will be ever so great."

665
00:53:17,780 --> 00:53:19,250
W-What?

666
00:53:19,250 --> 00:53:21,530
What are you saying right now?

667
00:53:21,530 --> 00:53:27,150
Didn't you say you will pass the Do Dang members' thoughts along to Her Highness after five days? Then why...?

668
00:53:28,000 --> 00:53:30,780
What are you doing?

669
00:53:30,780 --> 00:53:34,830
The Left Shi Joong is reading Her Highness's decree on her behalf.

670
00:53:34,830 --> 00:53:38,290
How can you be so disrespectful?

671
00:53:38,290 --> 00:53:41,330
They've already agreed on it in secret?

672
00:53:42,250 --> 00:53:46,750
What a failure this is. How can it be Crown Prince Chang?

673
00:53:46,750 --> 00:53:49,890
Jo Min Soo, you rascal...

674
00:53:57,500 --> 00:54:04,110
She also has ordered that the coronation take place on the last day of next month.

675
00:54:14,510 --> 00:54:16,670
Did you say fifteen days ago?

676
00:54:16,670 --> 00:54:18,080
Yes.

677
00:54:18,080 --> 00:54:21,310
Fifteen days ago, Hap Ha Lee In Gyeom passed away,

678
00:54:21,310 --> 00:54:24,530
and we even had his funeral.

679
00:54:29,230 --> 00:54:33,110
I received the request in Gyeongsanboo five days ago.

680
00:54:33,110 --> 00:54:38,960
He definitely said he received the request five days ago, but Lee In Gyeom was already dead fifteen days ago?

681
00:54:38,960 --> 00:54:42,210
How is it that you didn't report it to the Do Dang?

682
00:54:42,210 --> 00:54:44,130
I was going to,

683
00:54:44,130 --> 00:54:49,010
