684
00:54:50,910 --> 00:54:53,930
What? High treason?

685
00:54:55,390 --> 00:54:59,390
P-P-Please spare my life. I only did it because of a request.

686
00:55:02,540 --> 00:55:07,560
His hand... His hand wasn't that of a traveling merchant.

687
00:55:07,560 --> 00:55:10,500
Some scholar? Who is he?

688
00:55:10,500 --> 00:55:12,200
I'm not sure...

689
00:55:13,020 --> 00:55:16,950
He seemed like he was some relative.

690
00:55:16,950 --> 00:55:19,030
Speak clearly!

691
00:55:19,720 --> 00:55:24,340
Was there perhaps a burn on his wrist?

692
00:55:25,410 --> 00:55:28,890
Ah, yes. There was.

693
00:55:59,770 --> 00:56:02,590
Well, that is... I heard that during the meeting with the leaders of the army,

694
00:56:02,590 --> 00:56:06,170
while discussing about the next defense, Lee Seong Gye suddenly flew into a rage,

695
00:56:06,170 --> 00:56:10,450
and threw an ink pot right at you, General Jo...

696
00:56:14,840 --> 00:56:21,060
I've done as you said, but can we, the Gwon Moon Sae Jok, really stand up again?

697
00:56:24,470 --> 00:56:28,130
Reign of peace

698
00:56:28,130 --> 00:56:32,110
I did as you told me to, and now they are coming here to catch you ajussi.

699
00:56:32,110 --> 00:56:35,410
Yes, good job!

700
00:56:35,410 --> 00:56:37,470
Here's a yeot (taffy)!

701
00:56:37,470 --> 00:56:39,420
Now, go!

702
00:56:39,420 --> 00:56:41,830
Okay, let's begin the song again!

703
00:56:41,830 --> 00:56:45,470
♫ Since the eighteen offspring became the king

