00:57:07,710 --> 00:57:14,110
You have to make sure to deliver each secretly.

707
00:57:34,150 --> 00:57:37,850
'Chang', 'Geuk', 'Lee'

708
00:57:37,850 --> 00:57:40,410
'Chang' wins over 'Lee'?

709
00:57:41,380 --> 00:57:42,380
Could it be?

710
00:57:42,380 --> 00:57:46,180
We have to put Crown Prince Chang on the throne and keep Lee Seong Gye in check.

711
00:57:46,180 --> 00:57:49,580
We've all heard the "eighteen sons become the king", haven't we?

712
00:57:58,250 --> 00:58:03,050
Have we been played? Have we already been played?

713
00:58:08,030 --> 00:58:13,350
Yes, you have been played, colleague Sam Bong.

714
00:58:14,720 --> 00:58:16,420
It's him.

715
00:58:16,420 --> 00:58:17,720
What do you mean?

716
00:58:17,720 --> 00:58:25,900
That traveling merchant didn't do by request. He is the one that is behind all this.

717
00:58:25,900 --> 00:58:32,050
You were probably chasing after the dead Lee In Gyeom, so of course you have been played.

718
00:58:34,620 --> 00:58:39,100
You've been played by Ha Ryeun.
(Ha Ryeun, a schemer who later puts Lee Bang Won on the throne)

719
00:59:12,700 --> 00:59:14,770
Six Flying Dragons
Preview

720
00:59:14,770 --> 00:59:16,820
How is Sam Bong dangerous?

721
00:59:16,820 --> 00:59:19,980
To someone who has nothing but a hammer, everything in the world looks like nail to him.

722
00:59:19,980 --> 00:59:21,680
Sam Bong's hammer, the land system!

723
00:59:21,680 --> 00:59:25,040
Why do you not reveal to the world the incredible research you've done?

724
00:59:25,040 --> 00:59:29,180
It's something that's not going to happen! It's something that's never going to happen!

725
00:59:29,180 --> 00:59:32,520
There's a group that's trying to take Teacher Jo Joon's research. We have to bring it here safely.

726
00:59:32,520 --> 00:59:36,380
Taking the Gwon Moon Sae Jok's lands and distributing it equally among the country's common people.

727
00:59:36,380 --> 00:59:38,180
Wasn't that your dream?

728
00:59:38,180 --> 00:59:42,260
If you are really being sincere, then why don't you try kneeling?
